Package: doubleShrinker
Title: Double Shrinkage Empirical Bayes Estimators for Combining RCT and Observational Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("First", "Last", email = "first.last@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements double shrinkage empirical Bayes estimators that combine
    randomized controlled trial (RCT) and observational study data for multi-stratum
    subgroup causal effect estimation. Provides method of moments, MLE, and unbiased
    risk estimation approaches for hyperparameter estimation, along with competitor
    estimators and empirical Bayes confidence intervals.
